The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-22-2013 THURS






The Glenn Beck Program - 08/22/13 









The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET

 Also, the guys talk about the "accuracy" of Al Gore's global warming predictions.
